§3386.1. Definitions
As used in this Chapter, the following terms have the meaning ascribed to
them in this Section:
(1) "Addiction counselor" means any person who is licensed, certified, or
registered in accordance with the provisions of this Chapter and procedures
established by the board and who, by means of his special knowledge acquired
through formal education or practical experience, is qualified to provide addiction
counseling services to those individuals afflicted with or suffering from an addictive
